# Quick VHS test - record actual Claude TUI
Output vhs-claude-test.gif
Output vhs-claude-test.mp4

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "claude --dangerously-skip-permissions"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Type "What is 2+2? One word answer."
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "/exit"
Enter
Sleep 2s
